commit.message: band-aid v3caps, still crappy and broken, going to be redesigned shortly
add missing parameter to irc_set_sasl (thanks marchelzo)
add another way to STARTTLS right at the beginning of the connection.  only to be used when the ircd in question is known to support it that way
move more v3 stuff into v3 module
move irc_set_sasl and irc_set_starttls from irc.h to irc_ext.h
add STARTTLS support, not very pretty.  document later(TM)
add some more ircv3 capability negotiation, move (some) ircv3 related stuff into separate module
promote next_tok from util to common (now lsi_com_next_tok)
reluctantly add some first IRCv3 protocol support (message tags)
